<para style="q1">
<verse number="47" style="v" />Oh, think about how short my time is,</para>
<para style="q1">and for what uselessness you have created all the children of mankind!</para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="48" style="v" />Who can live and not die,</para>
<para style="q1">or rescue his own life from the hand of Sheol?
<char style="qs">Selah</char>
<note caller="u" style="s5"></note></para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="49" style="v" />Lord, where are your former acts of covenant faithfulness</para>
