<para style="q1">
<verse number="16" style="v" />Let your servants see your work,</para>
<para style="q1">and let our children see your majesty.
<note caller="u" style="s5"></note></para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="17" style="v" />May the favor of the Lord our God be ours;</para>
<para style="q1">prosper the work of our hands;</para>
