<note caller="u" style="s5"></note></para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="10" style="v" />No evil will overtake you;</para>
<para style="q1">no affliction will come near your home.</para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="11" style="v" />For he will direct his angels to protect you,</para>
