<note caller="u" style="s5"></note></para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="14" style="v" />Because he is devoted to me, I will rescue him.</para>
<para style="q1">I will protect him because he is loyal to me.</para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="15" style="v" />When he calls to me, I will answer him.</para>
<para style="q1">I will be with him in trouble;</para>
<para style="q1">I will give him victory and will honor him.</para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="16" style="v" />I will satisfy him with the length of his days,</para>
<para style="q1">and show him my salvation.
<note caller="u" style="s5"></note></para>
