<note caller="u" style="s5"></note></para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="8" style="v" />But you, Yahweh, will reign forever.</para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="9" style="v" />Indeed, look at your enemies, Yahweh!</para>
<para style="q1">Indeed, look at your enemies. They will perish!</para>
<para style="q1">All those who do evil will be scattered.
<note caller="u" style="s5"></note></para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="10" style="v" />You have lifted up my horn like the horn of the wild ox;</para>
