<note caller="u" style="s5"></note></para>
<chapter number="94" style="c" />
<para style="q1">
<verse number="1" style="v" />Yahweh, God who avenges,</para>
<para style="q1">God who avenges, shine over us.</para>
<para style="q1">
<verse number="2" style="v" />Rise up, judge of the earth,</para>
